Extend Spreading Breath	CATEGORY:FEAT	TYPE:Metabreath	VISIBLE:YES				PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.Breath Weapon	PREABILITY:2,CATEGORY=FEAT,Shape Breath,Spreading Breath								PRESTAT:1,CON=15					PRESIZEGTEQ:S				DESC:You can modify your breath weapon so that it fills a spread centered anywhere within a short distance of your head. The range and size of the spread depends on your size, as shown below. When you use this feat, add +2 to the number of rounds you must wait before using your breath weapon again.																	SOURCEPAGE:Drac						
