Power Dive	CATEGORY:FEAT	TYPE:General	VISIBLE:YES													PRESTAT:1,STR=15					PREMOVE:1,Fly=1	PREVARGTEQ:Maneuverability,3			DESC:When flying, you can dive and land on an opponent to deal extra damage. This is a standard action that can only affect creatures that are smaller than you. You make anoverrun attack, but the opponent cannot choose to avoid you. If you knock down the target, you may make an additional slam attack, dealing the indicated damage plus 1-1/2 times your Strength bonus (round down). This attack is at the usual +4 bonus against prone opponents.																	SOURCEPAGE:Drac						
